5. Conclusion
This chapter illustrated the real‚Äźtime implementation of Kalman filter in two applications, namely, the vision‚Äźbased vehicle tracking system and the GPS‚Äźaided SINU system. The Kalman filtering algorithm was derived with the consideration of real‚Äźtime element. Detail illustrations on deriving the Kalman filtering models for the vision‚Äźbased vehicle tracking system and the GPS‚Äźaided SINU system were outlined and discussed. Both implementations were put on real‚Äźtime experiments, and the results from both implementations were recorded and analyzed. The results show that the real‚Äźtime Kalman filtering algorithms work well in the applications.
